   "longContentPages" : [
"Welcome customer to the 3rd edition brochure of [REDACTED]'s medical station technologies, detailing all the possible ^orange;Enhancements^reset; that our medical personnel can bestow upon you.
As our staff will confirm, all procedures and fees are final, refunds are not available. For your safety, these modifications will not persist through a respawn chamber. Our available benefits are as follows:

^red;Berserker Rage^reset;: ^green;25% More^reset; Power, Increased Movement Speed. -^red;50^reset;% Knockback Resistance, -^red;35^reset; Protection.

^gray;Glass Cannon^reset;: ^green;100% More^reset; Damage at the cost of ^red;90% Less^reset; Protection

^green;Immunization^reset;: Provides ^cyan;immunity^reset; to most negative status effects. ^red;10% Less^reset; Power and Protection.

^white;Juggernaut^reset;: You become ^cyan;immune^reset; to knockback and gain ^green;50^reset; protection, but your movement speed is reduced by ^red;33%^reset;.

^green;Toxic Cloud^reset;: Every 3 seconds a ^green;toxic cloud^reset; that lasts 5 seconds and deals 30 piercing damage is released at your location. Every time this happens, you take ^red;5^reset; piercing damage. ^red;20^reset;% Increased Hunger Drain.

^#B200FF;Experiment #322^reset;: Applies random ^green;positive^reset; and/or ^red;negative^reset; statuses every 10 seconds which last 15-25 seconds.

^red;Trollblood^reset;: Regenerate ^green;40^reset;% of damage taken over 5 seconds, at the cost of ^red;20% Less^reset; HP and ^red;50^reset;% increased Energy Block Time.

^green;Renergizer^reset;: ^green;50% More^reset; Energy, ^green;33% More^reset; Energy Regeneration. Hunger Drain increased by ^red;25^reset;%. ^red;100^reset;% Increased Energy Block Time.

^yellow;Hypopanic^reset;: ^green;33% More^reset; Energy Regen, -^red;50^reset; Energy. In addition, Increased movement speed the less energy you have (up to +^green;67^reset;% speed at 35% energy remaining). Taking damage briefly ^red;stops^reset; energy regen, and ^red;consumes energy^reset; for 150% of damage.

^green;Hivemind^reset;: While over 10% health, drains ^red;0.1^reset;% of your Maximum Health to ^green;shoot a projectile^reset; at the closest enemy, prioritizing targets not hit recently, in a medium radius with a clear line of fire every 0.1 seconds, dealing ^green;0.5^reset;% of your Max HP as base damage (^orange;affected by power multiplier^reset;) on impact and causing ^red;Beestings^reset;.

^cyan;Mitochondria^reset;: Consumes ^red;2^reset; energy to regenerate ^green;1^reset; health every 0.15 seconds. Energy will regenerate only at full health.

^#7A7D81;Shadow Repel^reset;: Increases shadow resistance by ^green;50^reset;% and grants ^cyan;immunity^reset; to shadow status effects, but reduces the overall effectiveness of other resistances (except physical) by ^red;33^reset;%.

^#C5B00A;Radiation Repel^reset;: Increases radiation resistance by ^green;50^reset;% and grants ^cyan;immunity^reset; to radiation status effects, but reduces the overall effectiveness of other resistances (except physical) by ^red;33^reset;%.

^#69B115;Poison Repel^reset;: Increases poison resistance by ^green;50^reset;% and grants ^cyan;immunity^reset; to poison status effects, but reduces the overall effectiveness of other resistances (except physical) by ^red;33^reset;%.

^#A1F1FE;Ice Repel^reset;: Increases ice resistance by ^green;50^reset;% and grants ^cyan;immunity^reset; to ice status effects, but reduces the overall effectiveness of other resistances (except physical) by ^red;33^reset;%.

^#E99400;Fire Repel^reset;: Increases fire resistance by ^green;50^reset;% and grants ^cyan;immunity^reset; to fire status effects, but reduces the overall effectiveness of other resistances (except physical) by ^red;33^reset;%.

^#9711E4;Electrical Repel^reset;: Increases electric resistance by ^green;50^reset;% and grants ^cyan;immunity^reset; to electric status effects, but reduces the overall effectiveness of other resistances (except physical) by ^red;33^reset;%.

^#6062EB;Cosmic Repel^reset;: Increases cosmic resistance by ^green;50^reset;% and grants ^cyan;immunity^reset; to cosmic status effects, but reduces the overall effectiveness of other resistances (except physical) by ^red;33^reset;%."
